divs: Sighting DetailsThree friends doing an ATV ride in the mountains of Cordoba, Argentina, where most specialists agree there's a big UFO activity. We didn't see the object but it showed in our picture. No other picture has any mistake or problem. The camera is a SONY perfect functioning and never had a pic with any kind of light trouble.
